%BOM---------------------
Date:10/14/1997 9:53:00 PM
From:Terry Maynard

The "excavationaless sewer and pipeline rehabilitation" is a proprietary system
= process and materials = a sleeve that they install in sewers to stop leaks
and repair damage. The process is "trenchless" in that they do not dig up the
ground to get to the old pipes or damaged areas. Obviously, it saves the
municipality a lot of dollars if it can repair its pipes this way instead of
digging them up.

Good Investing!

Terry
